In [ ]:
def dtw(ts_x,ts_y,option=1):
    x_dim = len(ts_x)
    y_dim = len(ts_y)
    dtw_matrix = np.zeros((x_dim,y_dim))
    
    dtw_matrix[0,0] = abs(ts_x[0]-ts_y[0])

    for i in range(1,x_dim):
        dtw_matrix[i,0] = dtw_matrix[i-1,0] + abs(ts_x[i]-ts_y[0])

    for j in range(1,y_dim):
        dtw_matrix[0,j] = dtw_matrix[0,j-1] + abs(ts_y[j]-ts_x[0])
    
    for j in range(1,y_dim):
        for i in range(1,x_dim):
            dtw_matrix[i,j] = abs(ts_x[i]-ts_y[j]) + min(dtw_matrix[i-1,j-1],
                                                         dtw_matrix[i-1,j],
                                                         dtw_matrix[i,j-1])
    if option == 1:
        return dtw_matrix[x_dim-1,y_dim-1]
    else:
        return dtw_matrix

In [ ]:
classification = []

for i in x_scaled_test:

    a = dtw(i,barycenter_0)
    b = dtw(i,barycenter_1)
    c = dtw(i,barycenter_2)
    d = dtw(i,barycenter_3)

    if (a < b) & (a < c) & (a < d):
        classification.append(0)
    
    if (b < a) & (b < c) & (b < d):
        classification.append(1)
    
    if (c < a) & (c < b) & (c < d):
        classification.append(2)

    if (d < a) & (d < b) & (d < c):
        classification.append(3)
